{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "story_leizi_set_1", "eventName": "司雷霆者", "entryType": "NONE", "storyCode": null, "avgTag": "幕間", "storyName": "司雷霆者", "storyInfo": "一樁彈劾舊案，一位已經致仕的少卿，一項有悖炎律的正義之舉。大理寺麟青硯，肅政院太合、解真須在一個時辰內協商出最後的結果。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "25_g06_mountainroad_d", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$darkness01_intro", "key": "$darkness01_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_040", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "太合"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_040"}, {"id": 12, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_cloakmovement", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_041", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呼——", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_041"}, {"id": 18, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_040"}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "辛苦你跑一趟。", "name": "太合"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_040"}, {"id": 20, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_041"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "今天正好輪到我當值......", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_041"}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "太合，有什麼事情不能在肅政院的官署裡說？", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_041"}, {"id": 23, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_flag", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_039_1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_041", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_039_1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "原來還是為虞少卿的事。", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_041"}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "麟青硯少卿就這麼急於處置自己的前輩？", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_041"}, {"id": 33, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_039_1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這件事也是肅政院御史台的職責所在，解真御史未免太過怠慢。", "name": "麟青硯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_039_1"}, {"id": 35, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_041", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "解真"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_041"}, {"id": 37, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_040"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......是我召二位來此。", "name": "太合"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_040"}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "肅政院監察百官，縱然其人已致仕返鄉，在任期間所犯之事，也當追究法辦。", "name": "太合"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_040"}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當年虞澄少卿在彈劾琅珆知府時偽造證據一事，關係重大，二位此前已協商多次，未有定論。", "name": "太合"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_040"}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "約一個時辰後，虞澄少卿便會抵達此處......", "name": "太合"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_040"}, {"id": 44, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_041", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_039_1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你竟然瞞著我直接召回了他！", "name": "解真"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_041"}, {"id": 49, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_039_1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......不愧是太合。", "name": "麟青硯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_039_1"}, {"id": 51, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_040"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "此事不宜再拖。如何處置，二位須在一個時辰內有個定論。", "name": "太合"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_040"}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "若秉公斷案，那我等便於此間代三法司會審，當行炎律。", "name": "太合"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_040"}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "若施之以柔，虞少卿上山時，煩勞二位回避，讓我二人敘舊。", "name": "太合"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_040"}, {"id": 57, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "此山離京城不過二十里。入京之後，事情便再無轉圜的餘地。", "name": "太合"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_040"}, {"id": 58, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_041", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_039_1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "解真"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_041"}, {"id": 63, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_039_1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "麟青硯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_039_1"}, {"id": 65, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_041", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_039_1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_041", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我還是那句話，你未免太不講情理。", "name": "解真"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_041"}, {"id": 78, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_039_1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我也說過很多次了，麟青硯只是行大理寺少卿當行之事。", "name": "麟青硯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_039_1"}, {"id": 80, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "十年前，虞澄少卿巡檢天下刑獄，過琅珆時彈劾當地知府，曆一年三月，琅珆知府下獄身死。", "name": "麟青硯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_039_1"}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而我在整理卷宗時，發現了其中的疑點。", "name": "麟青硯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_039_1"}, {"id": 82, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "三個月前我去到琅珆，反覆查證......當年虞少卿彈劾所用的帳冊、名錄等關鍵物證，確實系偽造。", "name": "麟青硯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_039_1"}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這件事證據確鑿，辯無可辯。", "name": "麟青硯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_039_1"}, {"id": 84, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_041", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我並沒有要否認這樁舊案。", "name": "解真"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_041"}, {"id": 86, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只是請問少卿大人，那位琅珆知府，難道不該被彈劾嗎？", "name": "解真"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_041"}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他在任多年，欺上瞞下，侵吞朝廷撥款，是否屬實？", "name": "解真"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_041"}, {"id": 88, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他私發地方政令，屢次巧徵新稅，是否也是“辯無可辯”的事？", "name": "解真"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_041"}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他攔截伸冤的百姓，賄賂督察官員，虛報民情，又為禍一方了多長時間？", "name": "解真"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_041"}, {"id": 90, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "解真"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_041"}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "虞澄在彈劾狀上列舉了他十多條罪狀，有沒有哪一條是編造的呢？", "name": "解真"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_041"}, {"id": 92, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_039_1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "麟青硯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_039_1"}, {"id": 94, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "都屬實。", "name": "麟青硯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_039_1"}, {"id": 95, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_040"}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "虞少卿若是汙人清白，我等又何須在此相商？", "name": "太合"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_040"}, {"id": 99, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "琅珆知府彈劾案，牽連琅珆、京城及巡檢部門官員有嫌疑者近十人，經查俱無虛告，朝堂震動，地方肅然，風氣為之一改。", "name": "太合"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_040"}, {"id": 100, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_041", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_039_1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我聽說那陣子，百姓投來的感謝信函，在大理寺和肅政院碼了厚厚幾摞。", "name": "解真"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_041"}, {"id": 105, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "客觀來說，這難道不是一件大快人心的好事？", "name": "解真"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_041"}, {"id": 106, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "換言之，虞少卿所作所為，結果上難道不是有利於民？", "name": "解真"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_041"}, {"id": 107, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_039_1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "麟青硯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_039_1"}, {"id": 109, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_041", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "太合，你說呢？", "name": "解真"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_041"}, {"id": 111, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_040"}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "然。", "name": "太合"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_040"}, {"id": 115, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_041", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_039_1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "更何況，你似乎誤解了我的意思。", "name": "解真"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_041"}, {"id": 120, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我從來沒說不會處理這件事。", "name": "解真"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_041"}, {"id": 121, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_039_1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你所謂的處理......", "name": "麟青硯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_039_1"}, {"id": 123, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_041", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "大理寺會將虞澄從浩然閣中除名，戶部將追回他的致仕金，他返鄉後享有的一應優待，也將全部取消。", "name": "解真"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_041"}, {"id": 125, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "更者，如果虞澄的親眷將來入仕，朝廷也會多作考量。", "name": "解真"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_041"}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "同時，此事將知會刑部、肅政院及大理寺，三法司在任的所有大小官員，須引以為戒。", "name": "解真"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_041"}, {"id": 127, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果虞澄真是個大奸大惡之徒，用不著你說，在捉拿他下獄之前，我還得先用手裡這牽絲刃折磨他個十回八回。", "name": "解真"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_041"}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但他操勞一生，是人人稱頌的好官。他今年快七十了，我們姑且保他一個安穩的晚年，有何不可？", "name": "解真"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_041"}, {"id": 129, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_039_1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "秘而不宣，小懲小戒......對天下而言，其行未彰，其惡未誅。說什麼“有何不可”？", "name": "麟青硯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_039_1"}, {"id": 133, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_041", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "解真"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_041"}, {"id": 135, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_039_1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "太合，你覺得呢？", "name": "麟青硯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_039_1"}, {"id": 137, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_040", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_039_1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我......", "name": "太合"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_040"}, {"id": 142, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_039_1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......你也是這個想法？", "name": "麟青硯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_039_1"}, {"id": 144, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "太合，我清楚你的為人，是非分明，公事公辦，可從來沒有這麼多彎彎繞的心思，所以才能在離開軍伍後這麼快便升任監察御史......", "name": "麟青硯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_039_1"}, {"id": 145, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼這次？", "name": "麟青硯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_039_1"}, {"id": 146, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_040", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "青硯少卿過獎。", "name": "太合"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_040"}, {"id": 148, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "實不相瞞......", "name": "太合"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_040"}, {"id": 149, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "暫且不論官階，放下立場，我對虞少卿當年之所作所為，唯有欽佩。", "name": "太合"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_040"}, {"id": 150, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那知府劣跡斑斑，多年來，琅珆並非無人與之抗爭，卻最終無聲無息。", "name": "太合"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_040"}, {"id": 151, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "蓋因其行事滴水不漏，上下打點，手眼通天。若非別無他法，虞少卿何必出此下策？", "name": "太合"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_040"}, {"id": 152, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在那樁案子裡，他其實押上了自己的身家性命。", "name": "太合"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_040"}, {"id": 153, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如此浩然正氣，如此捨生忘死之英勇，不遜我那些沙場上的袍澤。", "name": "太合"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_040"}, {"id": 154, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_039_1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "麟青硯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_039_1"}, {"id": 156, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_040", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......所以，今日之事，只能交予二位定奪。", "name": "太合"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_040"}, {"id": 158, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_041", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘖，太合，我還挺欣賞你這柔情的一面的。", "name": "解真"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_041"}, {"id": 162, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_039_1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "麟青硯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_039_1"}, {"id": 164, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我同樣敬佩虞少卿的為人。", "name": "麟青硯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_039_1"}, {"id": 165, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們看到前面那棵樹了嗎？", "name": "麟青硯"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "25_g08_pavilion", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$m_sys_bitw_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 4.5}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "三人轉過一個山角，視野陡然開闊。"}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "太合與解真順著麟青硯的視線看過去，懸崖百丈，雲霧扼斷前路，一棵瘦直的松樹傲然挺立，露出積雪也掩藏不住的翠色。"}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_039_1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一年前，我剛從天師府來到大理寺，虞少卿是我最為敬慕的前輩。", "name": "麟青硯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_039_1"}, {"id": 182, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他要返鄉，我堅持送他一程，他繞路帶我來爬了這座山。", "name": "麟青硯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_039_1"}, {"id": 183, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_041", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "難怪你今天來得比我和太合都早。", "name": "解真"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_041"}, {"id": 185, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_039_1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那棵松樹，是他多年前親手種下的。", "name": "麟青硯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_039_1"}, {"id": 187, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_041", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "解真"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_041"}, {"id": 189, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_040", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "原來如此。", "name": "太合"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_040"}, {"id": 191, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_039_1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那時候的虞少卿還是個楞頭青，登高遠眺，眼前只有雲遮霧罩。猛然間陽光透過，將陰霾一掃而空，天地清朗......", "name": "麟青硯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_039_1"}, {"id": 193, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他想到自己馬上就要進入京城，赴大理寺就職，心裡面感慨萬千。", "name": "麟青硯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_039_1"}, {"id": 194, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他立誓要為天下人伸張正義，成為炎律的最後一道隘口，不讓任何人蒙冤受屈，於是種下一棵松苗以明心跡。", "name": "麟青硯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_039_1"}, {"id": 195, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_040", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好一個虞少卿！", "name": "太合"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_040"}, {"id": 197, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_039_1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是啊。那棵小小的松苗已經長成了如此挺拔的樹，前輩他也同樣對得起自己當年的抱負。", "name": "麟青硯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_039_1"}, {"id": 199, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "虞澄是大理寺有史以來最傑出的少卿，審冤斷錯無數，琅珆知府一案並不是他經手過最難的案子......", "name": "麟青硯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_039_1"}, {"id": 200, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他只錯了這一回。但他錯了這一回。", "name": "麟青硯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_039_1"}, {"id": 201, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_040", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "太合"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_040"}, {"id": 203, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_041", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一棵孤松長成這樣，多麼難得。", "name": "解真"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_041"}, {"id": 205, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "無論是誰，一路攀登，猛然看見有這麼一棵樹，挺身入雲，飽歷風雪而不折，心裡都會為之一振。", "name": "解真"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_041"}, {"id": 206, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "麟青硯少卿，推倒這一棵樹，會冷了多少登山之人的熱血呢？", "name": "解真"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_041"}, {"id": 207, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_039_1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "麟青硯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_039_1"}, {"id": 209, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_040", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "解真御史話中有話。", "name": "太合"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_040"}, {"id": 211, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_041", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我想要壓下這樁舊案，不單單是為了保下虞澄一人。", "name": "解真"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_041"}, {"id": 213, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "青硯少卿剛就任大理寺少卿不過一年，便徹查前任少卿的所有卷宗，在他致仕之後召回定罪。", "name": "解真"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_041"}, {"id": 214, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那下一任大理寺少卿，是不是上任後也該查一查你呢？", "name": "解真"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_041"}, {"id": 215, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_040", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "青硯少卿只是例行整理卷宗時偶然......", "name": "太合"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_040"}, {"id": 217, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_041", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是。但又有什麼區別？", "name": "解真"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_041"}, {"id": 219, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你我應該清楚得很，再清白的人，也經不起“查”。更何況是官身。", "name": "解真"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_041"}, {"id": 220, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_040", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "太合"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_040"}, {"id": 222, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_041", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們想想，如果這種事成了慣例，大小官員人人自危，心有遠慮，做起事情便會束手束腳。", "name": "解真"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_041"}, {"id": 224, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "畢竟一旦失之偏頗，就成了把柄。同僚也好，後繼者也好，指不定哪天被有心人發現，自己就得鋃鐺入獄。", "name": "解真"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_041"}, {"id": 225, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "長此以往，誰還敢在任上有所作為？", "name": "解真"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_041"}, {"id": 226, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_039_1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "麟青硯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_039_1"}, {"id": 228, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_041", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "青硯少卿，三法司不是天師府，我們往往要權衡更多東西。", "name": "解真"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_041"}, {"id": 230, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_039_1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "解真，你何必偷換概念？", "name": "麟青硯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_039_1"}, {"id": 232, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "身為大理寺少卿，偽造證據，這件事的性質，到了你口中，竟然只是“失之偏頗”？", "name": "麟青硯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_039_1"}, {"id": 233, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_041", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "解真"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_041"}, {"id": 235, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_039_1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "更何況，你的說法，恕我難以苟同。", "name": "麟青硯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_039_1"}, {"id": 237, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_041", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯？", "name": "解真"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_041"}, {"id": 239, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_039_1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "未有作為，而思保全？", "name": "麟青硯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_039_1"}, {"id": 241, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我幼年初學雷法，天師便教導我，“司雷霆者，必先敬畏其威，否則必有自傷之日”。", "name": "麟青硯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_039_1"}, {"id": 242, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "三法司中，肅政院監察百官，大理寺覆核刑獄，每個官員、每樁案子，後面都需要一雙眼睛、一道隘口。", "name": "麟青硯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_039_1"}, {"id": 243, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那我們這些行監察之職的人，身後是不是也需要另一雙眼睛、另一道隘口呢？世上沒有完美的制度，不可能這樣層疊循環下去。", "name": "麟青硯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_039_1"}, {"id": 244, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以我們這些人，最先應該監察的，其實是自己。不然如何保證律法能真正護佑每一個炎國百姓？", "name": "麟青硯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_039_1"}, {"id": 245, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們都在三法司當差，你未必不清楚這個道理！", "name": "麟青硯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_039_1"}, {"id": 246, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_041", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "難道，法不容情？", "name": "解真"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_041"}, {"id": 248, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "絕情的究竟是你，還是炎律？！", "name": "解真"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_041"}, {"id": 249, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_039_1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "執炎律者，若有律不依，那立炎律何用？！", "name": "麟青硯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_039_1"}, {"id": 251, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_040", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "二位不必如此過激......", "name": "太合"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_040"}, {"id": 253, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_039_1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我必須追究這樁舊案，同樣不單單是為了處置虞澄一人。", "name": "麟青硯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_039_1"}, {"id": 255, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_041", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "解真"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_041"}, {"id": 257, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_039_1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "虞少卿當年在琅珆，面對那個劣跡斑斑卻滴水不漏的知府，為了伸張正義，不得已用了“偏頗”的手段，似乎情有可原。", "name": "麟青硯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_039_1"}, {"id": 259, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "換作你我，未必不會做出同樣的選擇。", "name": "麟青硯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_039_1"}, {"id": 260, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可如果日後我們面對的是更加曖昧的情況呢？可如果日後我們有意為惡呢？", "name": "麟青硯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_039_1"}, {"id": 261, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是否更容易動用些“偏頗”的手段，去放過一個壞人，去構陷一個好人？", "name": "麟青硯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_039_1"}, {"id": 262, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "畢竟，為惡，要簡單得多。", "name": "麟青硯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_039_1"}, {"id": 263, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "國之法度，定人生死。你我身在其位，便容不得半點行差踏錯！", "name": "麟青硯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_039_1"}, {"id": 264, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_041", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "解真"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_041"}, {"id": 266, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_040", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "太合"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_040"}, {"id": 268, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_040", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "青硯少卿所言，讓人醍醐灌頂。", "name": "太合"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_040"}, {"id": 272, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "律法面前，無“事宜從權”一說，這還是太傅當年對我的教誨。", "name": "太合"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_040"}, {"id": 273, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "若因對虞少卿的欽佩之情，有傷炎律之儀......因私廢公，是我荒唐了。", "name": "太合"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_040"}, {"id": 274, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_040", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "算來，虞少卿也該到了。", "name": "太合"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_040"}, {"id": 278, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "解真御史可還有話說？", "name": "太合"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_040"}, {"id": 279, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_041", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "解真"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_041"}, {"id": 281, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "話都說到了這份上......這樁案子由青硯少卿提起，決定權當然也在她。", "name": "解真"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_041"}, {"id": 282, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我承認你說的在理。", "name": "解真"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_041"}, {"id": 283, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但最後還是想請二位想想，彈劾虞澄，相比當年彈劾那位琅珆知府，影響只大不小。", "name": "解真"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_041"}, {"id": 284, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_040", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "太合"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_040"}, {"id": 286, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "既然如此，請少卿定奪。", "name": "太合"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_040"}, {"id": 287, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_039_1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所謂法者，便是懸在人們心上與頭頂的那道雷。", "name": "麟青硯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_039_1"}, {"id": 291, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雷聲驚蟄，天地通明。", "name": "麟青硯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_039_1"}, {"id": 292, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "若此雷不落，麟青硯難為大理寺少卿。", "name": "麟青硯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_039_1"}, {"id": 293, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_thunders_amb", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 1.0, "g": 1.0, "b": 1.0, "fadetime": 0.05, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_flag", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "白日驚雷，羽獸驟起疾飛，積雪從枝椏間撲簌簌落下，那棵青松依然挺拔，又多了幾分翠色。"}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "山下，遠來的客人剛剛下車。他怔怔抬頭，良久未曾挪動一步。"}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}